sentences.en: " Our Pearl is a fitful and fantastic little elf sometimes.

sentences.en: An infamous elf wizard from long ago returns as a lich.

sentences.en: Conclusions: Elf - 1 expression in endometrial carcinoma correlates with the malignant potential of this tumor.

sentences.en: Detection of Elf - 1 and Rb proteins expression may be useful for early diagnosis.

sentences.en: ELF waves from HAARP when targeted on areas can weather - engineer and create mood changes affecting millions.

sentences.en: I wanted to believe like I believed last year — that Santa was a big fat elf in a red suit.

sentences.en: Introduce the information of the header file - ELF and the process of running ELF file under LINUX.

sentences.en: Objective : To study the expression of Elf - 1 c - erbB 2 in normal, atypical hyperplastic and malignant endometrium.

sentences.en: Objective To explore the relationship between extremely low frequency ( ELF ) magnetic fields and carcinogenesis.

sentences.en: Some of those children were fair and rounded, others dark and elf - like.
sentences.cn: 这些孩子当中,有的白晰圆胖, 有的黑而窈窕.

sentences.en: The distribution of cell cycle time in ELF magnetic fields and at different temperatures are investigated.

sentences.en: The expression of Elf - 1 and Rb protein were not significantly different in several epidermal malignant tumor.

sentences.en: When I was done with the bar, I worked as a hospital porter, a market research cold-caller, an elf in Santa's Grotto in Harrods and a runner in a porno post-production company.

sentences.en: Xia has created a mediaeval town full of elf princesses and knights, a busy modern city with young students pursuing dreams, and a quiet ancient town with innocent children and mysterious legends.
sentences.cn: 夏达的笔下有满是精灵公主和武士的中世纪小镇，有青年学生逐梦的繁华都市，有生活着一群天真儿童，蕴藏神秘传说的宁静古镇。
